# ============================================================================
# WHAT GETS COMMITTED (EXAMPLES)
# ============================================================================
# These files ARE committed and are generic for all users:
#
# ✅ README.md                    - Project documentation
# ✅ docker-compose.yml           - Container configuration
# ✅ Dockerfile                   - Custom image build
# ✅ config/birdnet.conf.example  - Template configuration
# ✅ docs/                        - Documentation
# ✅ scripts/                     - Setup and utility scripts
# ✅ CONTRIBUTING.md              - Contribution guidelines
# ✅ LICENSE                      - License file
# ✅ .github/                     - Issue templates
#
# ❌ config/birdnet.conf          - Your personal configuration
# ❌ config/BirdSongs/            - Your bird recordings
# ❌ config/*_species_list.txt    - Your local species lists
# ❌ ssl/*.key                    - Your SSL certificates
#
# ============================================================================